The evidence with the title 'West virginia employee's withholding exemption certificate form wv/it ... ' says If you are single, Head Of Household, or married and your spouse does not work, and you are receiving wages from only one job , and you wish to have your tax withheld at alower rate , you must check the box on line 5 . When requesting withholding from pension and annuity payments you must present this completed form . 
